# Cotton Swatch Card, Color of the Year 2023, 18-1750 Viva Magenta

## The definitive color standard for cotton

Sku#: 18-1750X

$ 15.90

Add To Cart

Pantone’s Cotton Swatch Card is the cotton color standard for designers, colorists, and product developers in apparel, textiles, and soft home. Now available in the Pantone Color of the Year for 2023, PANTONE 18-1750 VIVA MAGENTA is a brave and fearless red shade demonstrating a new signal of strength. Individual swatch cards are made from double-layered, 100% cotton poplin, loose-format fabric. Made to exacting color specifications, each swatch card includes a barcode that can be used to order the associated spectral data for assured color accuracy in production.

All Swatch Cards are non-returnable/non-refundable.

